#	Configuration file for the gravitational physics module:
#	gravitational field caused by a point mass of mass (ptmass) at
#       position (ptxpos) in the ptdirn direction.  The point mass is
#	assumed to be distant, allowing the field to be treated as
#	plane-parallel.

D ptmass        mass of the point
D ptxpos        location of the point mass, in the ptdirn direction
D ptdirn        x = 1, y = 2, z = 3
D gravsoft      softening length

PARAMETER ptmass       REAL    10000.
PARAMETER ptxpos       REAL    1.
PARAMETER ptdirn       INTEGER 1
PARAMETER gravsoft     REAL    .0001

